My main (56 druid) is a 224 tailor, and have been looking to make this. Problem is that 2 of the 3 items needed are insanely rare, and one of them are nodrop.<br>
You need a nodrop tunic from the robe guys in ME or Akheva, thats what im looking for at the moment, seen boots and leg drop so far. No drop, so the tailor NEED to loot. Chance of a 210+ tailor being there when one drop are around 0.<br>
<br>
If you by some freak chance found a tailor that had that part, you would need mind worm hides. Mind worms hides drop in ME and Akheva (might be other places too, not sure, doubt it). <br>
ME it drop from the burrower types thats triggered in traps (might be rare spawn too, not sure). Burrowers not that bad, but the mind worms from the traps are NASTY, mana sucking beasts).<br>
In akheva they drop form the mind worms (from traps), and the burrower types.<br>
<br>
Problem is that NOONE hunt the mind worms. Theyre triggered in traps, and taps mana, so only released on a major accident, and usually people zone if they trigger them. <br>
People can hunt the burrower types in Akheva, my guild hunted them for 4 hours trying to spawn the Insanity Crawler. Loot were: 57 mind worm meats, 10 spells, 7 mind worm hides.<br>
Yes, 7 hides from chain pulling 2 at a time for 4 hours with a 30+ person raid. Luckily im guilds only tailor, so got all 7. My guess would be that they are as rare in ME too, never seen one drop there.<br>
<br>
Never seen a mind worm hide for sale, and never met anyone who ever seen one, apart from the 7 we got in guild, and 1 a friend of mine got from a mind worm train in akheva.<br>
<br>
Chance of 210+ tailor BOTH getting 3 mind worm hides (due to mana drains you cant get a group to hunt the ones from traps, and the burrowers nasty), and the nodrop tunic will be VERY close to non existing. <br>
<br>
Personally i doubt any exist on Veeshan at all, unless theres a japanese master tailor i dont know anything about. I am aiming at getting one for my monk someday, and if i were ever to sell it, i doubt price would be under 50K, both due to nice stats and due to incredible rarity. <p><br>Hesten Gnyffa, level 56 druid, tradeskill master, Veeshan server<br>
